Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.47,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:37.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.11,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:15.25,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:22.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.33,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:34.27,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:03.43,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...then Lebrand picked up the scythe, and cleared with it a circular space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:08.44,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...three or four yards in diameter, just below the insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:13.52,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Then he told Jupiter to let the string go, and come down from the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Next, Miss Misonoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.72,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Lebrand placed a small stick into the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.99,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...at the exact place where the insect was buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:33.54,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,He took from his pocket a long tape measure. He fastened it down and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Resign, of your own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tolerate such an injustice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:49.77,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...he went in front of his master, clearing away the bushes with a spade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, that will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You seem unwell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Miss Yoshimoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.77,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,At the distance of fifty feet, Lebrand stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.64,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...and put the second stick into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:16.48,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,The ground around it was again cleared in a large circle, about four feet deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"The unqualified person should leave the Sorority.."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Such poor losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a nice Kyoto-style coffee shop at the train station!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good. Their shiratama is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to throw these in the incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them in my desk this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,7. The Darkness in the Clock Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what's so hateful about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be liked by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be liked just a little, enough not to be hurt, or to hurt someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was enough and is still enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why am I hated so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...by so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is... What on earth is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So... this is the clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"M-sama, thinking of you has turned me into ashes."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Say you love me once again. That will restore the life in me."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been many before me who came here to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When they lost their courage to continue, they would come to this dark tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When they lost love, and when they lost friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They found, in this tower, a place to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...to embrace themselves and wet their knees with their warm tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, the year before last, and many many years before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So many sisters over these many years, coming here to share their pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoking... she's smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She... she is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick them up, won't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This must have been the sound I heard earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many marks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...this silhouette!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miya-sama! It's a silhouette of Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They are so deep and so... many.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the rains which fall in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...the tears also fall in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it for, the sadness which creeps into my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sadness for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sadness for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The name has an echo of loneliness in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And about Saint-Juste-sama and Miya-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is a mystery between them I cannot understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...the tears fall in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who named her Saint-Juste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who on earth... is Saint Juste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have twelve minutes to catch that train, or I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve Minutes! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to go home together with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the Sorority, she has a lot of socializing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear from her directly! Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Being her friend, can't you understand why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she asked me to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd not be so easily hurt if she told me herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... call you some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go shopping for material for the pajamas we're sewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for home economics class...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's early next week. So let's go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well... I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy with something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sort of... the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find a book there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't go today, I'd have to go next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You hard worker, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! You're in a jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll choose your pattern too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you can go to the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're caught, you'll be suspended from school... or expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I adore expulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take those.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I adore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your wound still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it on the shelf over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! The shelf over there? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to learn about The French Revolution and Saint-Juste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! But... but how...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The freshmen will all be in front of these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on the French Revolution and Saint-Juste in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading for any reason is always better then not reading at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, there's this, and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I saw Ide-san and Kooriyama-san at the Paris Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And then? What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know Urayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a library. If you want to talk, go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'd like to borrow these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One can't even read peacefully in the library these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You like books so much, Kaoru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that from someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei was transferred into our school in junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to always be alone, reading books...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...showing no interest in her surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it wouldn't interest you... being such an athlete...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Verlaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"As rain falls..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I recruited Rei for our basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She played basketball!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She easily became a star player.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She had such life in her when she was playing basketball...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and her eyes glowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I liked watching her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...or so I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what really attracted me to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...was something inhuman in her nature;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and those eyes with such a distant, far-away look...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she see so far away? What lies deep within her soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookies are baking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes... it must be from Tomoko's cooking club...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Making overtures not only to Miya-sama, but now to Kaoru-no-Kimi as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You took after your mother the "hostess"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...who will... with anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. You left it at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the incinerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that... Miss Sorority has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Nanako! Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What did you do to Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-hat? We didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! She just fell down by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you mess with Nanako, you'll be facing me for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever treat her mean you'll be dealing with me. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:21:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leon de Saint-Juste was a young knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At eighteen, his heart broken by love, he was a dissolute young Parisian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He attended Darcy University and studied Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After the French Revolution he joined with Robespierre of the Jacobin Club
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And he sent many of the nobility and royalty to the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,His feminine beauty and cruelty made him both feared and hated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he became known as the "Angel of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1794 his party lost power,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...and at age 24, he was guillotined alongside his friend, Robespierre.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the rains which fall in this world, tears also fall in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it creeping into my heart, filling it with sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Saint-Juste of the French Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He gazed into death, even his own, with cool detachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does her nickname reveal the sad vision which is reflected in her eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a vision of Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:14.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:19.52,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:25.12,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:30.60,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:36.87,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:42.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.34,0:24:45.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:47.88,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:50.28,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:55.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko gives an extravagant birthday party...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.56,0:25:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Nanako is the only guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After the party, Mariko invites Nanako to her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanako is in for much more than she bargained for...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.51,0:25:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: I Want You...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.66,0:25:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
